I've seen exceptions be made for forum &quot;regulars&quot; many, many times, while other, newer members (who may have been reading others' posts for a while and used those to guage the &quot;limits&quot; for things like this) are given less tolerance for the same or lesser vulgarities. It really is a double standard. <br>
<br>
I think you guys do a great job, but honestly, the profanity level of regular posts has risen to the point that I enjoy reading this board far less today than I did three years ago. Please enforce this rule more strongly - I think it would improve the quality of the posting and the tolerance people have for each other. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lordbug>LordBug</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br>  Posts: 696<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/6/03 9:53:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26402.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://lordbug.hypermart.net/icon3.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What can we do to improve the message boards?</span><hr size=1> &gt;What can we do to improve the overall Graffe message board experience?<br>
<br>
The messageboards, I think, could use some consolidation.  We have too many forums right now.  We don't need as many as we have now, and definately won't need half of them once the Arcanist/Graffe merger actually happens.<br>
<br>
&gt;What can we do to become better moderators?<br>
<br>
Ban all gnomes. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Seriously, I think you guys are doing a great job moderating.<br>
<br>
&gt;What can we do to get the community back on track?<br>
<br>
Get the Arcanist/Graffe merger done.  It's way overdue.  The forums are nice for information, but clunky.  A main website that has all of our pooled knowledge on quests, spells, research, etc. is sorely needed.<br>
<br>
I guess forumwise, I don't want a whole lot.  I more want to see the merger completed.  That alone, IMO, will greatly improve the community. <p><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26448">Ebdain Ahriman</a><BR>
